column6: [{"Question":"TotalScore","Answer":"4"},{"Question":"Additional comments:","Answer":"Work on the project was exactly what I needed.  Someone to take charge, be flexible, and evaluate our business activities to calculate our tax incentive.  The PM on our project was so courteous, professional, and very respectful of our time.  The only area that could improve was the back office responses to our vendor management team requests."}]

column6: [{"Question":"TotalScore","Answer":"5"},{"Question":"Additional comments:","Answer":"Coming into this the learning curve seemed steep and a little complicated but Anna Doran and the rest of the team did an awesome job of explaining and simplifying everything. We weren't sure how much time was going to have to be put into the effort but Anna did an incredible job of asking us the right questions and talking to the right people in our office resulting in the amount of time spent being less than expected. The end result was great for us and we are excited to continue our partnership with CTI."}]
